Cell Collective e fumaneha ka bolokolohi hore e sebelisoe ke sechaba sa thuto le se se nang phaello. Tšebeliso ea Cell Collective ka har'a mekhatlo e ts'ireletso ea chelete e ka hloka tumellano e eketsehileng ea tumello. Ka kopo ikopanye le support@cellcollective.org bakeng sa boitsebiso bo eketsehileng.

Lingoliloeng tse hlahang ho sebelisoa ha Cell Collective li lokela ho amohela http://www.cellcollective.org e le mohloli oa dintlha tseo mme o qotsa pampiri e latelang: Helikar et. al. 2012. BMC Syst Biol. 6:96. doi: 10.1186 / 1752-0509-6-96.

Landing.ColumnBanner.BuildModelsDescript: Tšoaea mekhoa e mengata ea likokoana-hloko, ho kenyeletsa marang-rang a mefuta-futa, melao ea liphatsa tsa lefutso, phetoho ea pontšo, marang-rang a ho sebelisana le cell-cell, li-webs tsa lijo, joalo-joalo tse amanang le likokoana-hloko tse sa tšoaneng tse tsoang libaktheria ho ea likokoana-hloko ho ea ho limela ho limela ho batho. Hlalosa mehlala e sa hlokahalang ho kena kapa ho fetola maemo a rarahaneng a lipalo.
Landing.ColumnBanner.PerformStimulations: Sebelisa nako ea sebele, ho sebelisana ka tsela e tšoanang ho bona ka tsela e bonts'etso ea matla a sebetsang tlasa maemo a sa tšoaneng a extracellular hammoho le maemo a macha (e leng, a kula). Tsamaea liteko tse makholo tsa ho etsisa ka taba ea metsotso e seng mekae 'me u etse tlhahlobo ea tlhahiso-phallo ho bona likarabo tsa lik'hamera tlas'a maemo a sa tšoaneng
Landing.ColumnBanner.AnalyzeResultsDescr: Hlahloba lits'ebeletso le likarabo tsa lik'hemik'hale tlasa maemo a fapaneng. Tsamaisa lisebelisuoa tsa khatello ea tsamaiso ea tsamaiso-kholo ho bolela esale pele le ho beha boemo ba motho ka mong le likarolo tsa likarolo tsa tsamaiso. Hlalosa le ho hlahloba lithethefatsi tse reretsoeng ho e-na le morero oa ho ipapisa le lithethefatsi.

Dashboard.joyrideStepsHomePhase1.Publish:
• E BOLETSWE MODELS ke mekhoa e hlahlojoang ke lithaka, e hatisitsoeng e fumanoang Sechabeng sa Colle Collective bakeng sa lipapiso le monehelo o eketsehileng.
  • MODELISO EA KA e na le mehlala e hahiloeng le eo u nang le eona.
  • TSEBA LE 'ME ke mehlala eo ba bang ba sebelisanang le uena ka ho toba. Sebelisa tšobotsi ena ho haha ​​le ho hlahloba ka ho toba mehlala le barupelli ba hao (ntle le ho romela lifaele tsa SBML tsa moelelo morao le holimo)
  • Khutsa ka ho le Letona ho bona Mefuta e meng!
Dashboard.joyrideStepsHomePhase1.YouMayC: U ka tobetsa {photo} icon ka nako efe kapa efe ho ithuta ka likarolo tse ngata tsa Cell Collective.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsModelPhase1.ClickO: Tobetsa letšoao ho fetola pakeng tsa {photo1} (Sheba Leihlo) le {photo2} (Hlakola Mode). <ol> <li> Kopa Kakhefa sebakeng se se nang letho ho kenya karolo e ncha. </ li> <li> Double Click Label ho renama karolo. </ li> <li> Shift + ka ho le letona ho tlanya pakeng tsa hare kapa ka hare likarolo tse ka hare. </ li> <li> Fetola pakeng tsa ho sebelisana hantle kapa hampe ka Shift + ka ho panya-pota moleng oa ho hokahanya. </ li> </ ol>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsModelPhase1.NewMod: Lisebelisoa tse ncha tsa mohlala li ka boela tsa kenngoa ka ho tobetsa mona ho {photo}. Tlanya lebokose ka bobeli ho fetola lebitso la motsoako.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsModelPhase1.ToAddA: <span> Ho kenya activator kapa inhibitor, hula le ho theola likarolo tsa lethathamo la Internal Components kapa likarolo tse ka ntle ho lebokose le nang le tokelo ea Drop Component box. </ span>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsModelPhase1.ClickO: Tobetsa ho {photo} icon ho boloka liphetoho tsa hau.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsSimulationPhase1.U: <span> Sebelisa slide e bonolo ho beha maemo a ka thōko (e leng sepheo sa ho etsisa). Litekanyo li ka boela tsa fetoha nakong ea ho etsisa ho bona eka liphetoho tsa tsamaiso ea nako e ntse e le teng. Sena se tšoana le ho fapana ha tikoloho ea tsamaiso ea likokoana-hloko le ho bona karabo ea eona. </ span>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsSimulationPhase1.S: Khetha lebokose le ka tlaase ho letšoao la setšoantšo {photo} bakeng sa lisebelisoa tseo u batlang ho li bona ka Sekhahla sa Simulation. Hovering holim'a lebokose la motsoako o tla totobatsa mokhoa oa eona, ho u lumella hore u fumane kapele mothating oa setšoantšo se phathahaneng!
Dashboard.joyrideStepsSimulationPhase1.C: Tobetsa {photo1} letšoao ho qala simulation. U ka boela ua tobetsa {photo2} ho emisa sekhetho ka nako leha e le efe kapa u tsosolose setšoantšo ka ho totobatsa setšoantšo sa {photo3}.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsAnalysisPhase1.Cli: Tobetsa letšoao la {photo} ho theha teko e ncha. Liteko li rehiloe ka ho toba ka ho tobetsa lebokose.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsAnalysisPhase1.Use: <span> Sebelisa slide e bonolo ho beha maemo a ka thōko (e leng lipehelo tsa ho etsisa) bakeng sa teko. Sena se ts'oana le ho beha lipontšo tsa kantle ho tsamaiso ea likokoana-hloko sebakeng sa eona, ho susumetsa tsela eo li arabelang ka eona. </ span>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsAnalysisPhase1.Cli: Tobetsa ho {photo} iicon ho qala simulation.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsAnalysisPhase1.Dos: <span> Likarabo tsa lipotso li ka hlahisoa bakeng sa karolo leha e le efe ea mohlala ka ho khetha karolo e loketseng bakeng sa X le Y-axis. Ka kakaretso, motsoako o ka ntle o emeloa ho X-axis (phapang ea pente) empa likarolo tse ka hare li emeloa ka-axis (mefuta e tsitsitseng). Mekhoa e mengata ea karabo e ka hlahisoa ho tsoa tekong e le 'ngoe. </ span>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsHomePhase2.YouMayS: <span> O ka batlisisa mehlala ka sehlooho, tlhaloso, tag kapa lebitso la protheine. Potso e le 'ngoe e tla batlisisa Mekhoa e hatisitsoeng, Mekhoa ea Ka, le ho arolelana le' na likaroloana ka nako e le 'ngoe. </ Span>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsHomePhase2.ChangeB: Fetola pakeng tsa Lintlha le Grid View
Dashboard.joyrideStepsHomePhase2.YouCanC: <span> O ka fetola pono ea hau pakeng tsa lethathamo le pono ea grid. </ span>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsHomePhase2.InThisM: <span> Ketsahaleng ena u ka fetola pono ea hau ea mosebedisi, fetola password ea hau, le ho kena. </ span>
JoyDashboardRide.joyrideStepsModelPhase2: <span> Melao (kapa SubConditions) e sebelisetsoa ho etsa mohlala oa ts'ebelisano kapa ho arolelana mekhoa ea ho itšunya-tšunya pakeng tsa molekane a le mong kapa ba fetang balekane. Tobetsa ho eketsa letšoao ho bula Lenane la maemo, hula le ho theola likarolo tse nepahetseng lebokoseng la lipuisano le ho hlalosa hore na Boemo bo lokela ho sebetsa kapa bo sa sebetse. </ span>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsModelPhase2.Addind: Ho eketsa le ho kenya Litlaleho
Dashboard.joyrideStepsModelPhase2.ClickO: Mehlala e hlalositsoe mme e hlalosoa ka ho sebelisa Base ea Tsebo. Tobetsa {photo1} ho eketsa dikahare le {photo2} ho eketsa lintlha. Kenya Phatlalatso ea PubMed (PMID) feela hore u etse sebopeho se khutsitseng mme u kenyelelane litemana. Litlhaloso li ka thehoa ho ea ka khatiso le mofuta oa data. Tlanya ka ho le letona feela ho sethaleng 'me u khethe lebokose leo u batlang ho le eketsa.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsModelPhase2.Collab: Tšebelisano ke senotlolo sa li sibollo tse ncha ho sebelisa mekhoa ea mekhoa e metle - 'me e ka pelong ea Sehlopha sa Selekane! Ho tobetsa {photo} ho u fetisetsa leqepheng la Share, ho u nolofalletsa ho eketsa barupeluoa, ho etsa marang-rang a kopantsoeng le ho phatlalatsa liteko.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsModelPhase2.Select: <span> Khetha karolo eo u ka ratang ho e fetola. Ho tobetsa lebokose hang-hang ke phetoho ea ho lahleheloa ke mosebetsi (e bontsitsoeng ke lebokose le khubelu), mme ho tobetsa lebokose ka makhetlo a mabeli ke phetoho ea ts'ebeliso ea mosebetsi (e bontšitsoeng ke letšoao le botala). Ho penya ka lekhetlo la boraro ho tlosa phetoho eo. Liphetoho tsa lefutso li ka kenyelletsoa pele kapa ka nako ea ho etsisa ho bona eka liphetoho li teng ka nako ea sebele. </ span>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsSimulationPhase2.C: Tobetsaonjezohuts obediong ea kutumikira naha. Hang ha boemo ba pele bo bōptjoa, letšoao le bontšoa ka har'a karolo ea Internal Components. Ho tloha khoeling ena, khetha likarolo tseo u li batlang ho sebetsa qalong ea se tšoanang (t = 0).

Tobetsa {photo} ho tlaleha phallo ea simulation. Setšoantšo se tla fetoha se tala hang ha ho rekota ho ntse ho rekota. Liphetoho maemong a liteko kapa liphetoho, le nako ea bona ea nako ea nako-nako, li tlalehiloe li bolokiloe ka potlako ea ho lumellana, e leng ho nolofalletsang ho khutlisetsa liteko tsa preset.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsAnalysisPhase2.Mul: <span> Liteko tse ngata li ka khethoa ho sebelisa li-checkboxes. Hang ha u khethiloe, u ka tlosa, kopitsa, kapa ua boela ua leka liteko tseo ka nako e le 'ngoe. Sena ke sa bohlokoa haholo bakeng sa ho ntlafatsa liteko ha u se u entse phetoho tsamaisong ea tsamaiso ea mohlala. </ span>,
Dashboard.joyrideStepsAnalysisPhase2.Col: Tobetsa {photo} haufi le Phallo ea Sekhahla: lebokose ho bopa phallo ea simulation. Ho hlahlojoa ha lipalangoang ha hoa ka ha tlalehoa, ka hona, maemo a ka ntle (e leng lipeo) kapa liphetoho, 'me mefuta ea bona (e leng nako ea nako-e leng teng) e lokela ho ba e hlalositsoeng ka letsoho. Bala thupelo ea Phallo ea Simulation bakeng sa lintlha tse ling.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsAnalysisPhase2.Onc: <span> Hang ha o se o na le graph e hlahisitsoeng mona o ka kopitsa Labor Relations Graph e le faele ea PNG ka ho tobetsa mona. </ span>
